Cell["\<\
Hence this automorphism moves a point in \
\[DoubleStruckCapitalP](t123,p3,u1,s1) with p3 == A1, u1 == A1^2, s1 == 1 to \
a point in \[DoubleStruckCapitalP](t123,p3,u1,s1)  with p3 == u1 == 0, s1 == \
1. It moves a point in \[DoubleStruckCapitalP](t123,p3,u1,s1) with p3 == A1, \
u1 == A1^2, s1 == 1, t123==0 to the s1-point.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.984715461330696*^9, 3.9847154927476254`*^9}, {
  3.9847155255945415`*^9, 3.9847155817250137`*^9}, {3.984715811565674*^9, 
  3.984715840346674*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"6b4538c8-11e5-5945-bce9-\
36495bb865e3"]
}, Open  ]],

