Cell["\<\
Hence this automorphism moves a point in \[DoubleStruckCapitalP] (s1, t123, \
t135) with  t123== A2, s1 == 1 to a point  in \[DoubleStruckCapitalP] (s1, \
t123, t135)  with t123==0, s1 == 1. It moves a point in \
\[DoubleStruckCapitalP] (s1, t123, t135) with t135==0, t123== A, s1 == 1  to \
the s1 - point .\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.984716557710846*^9, 3.9847167674247837`*^9}, {
  3.984717129330488*^9, 3.9847171350048523`*^9}, {3.984717172244999*^9, 
  3.9847172144354534`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"c6071b27-8229-834d-8378-\
c6ab381d00c3"]
}, Open  ]],

