Cell["\<\
Thus the coefficient of s246 in the 1 st equation of Codim2No501 is \
invertible near the flipping and flipped loci . We denote this coefficient by \
1/U246, where U246 is a unit with 1 as the degree 0 term near the flipping \
and flipped loci.  By the implicit function theorem, we may consider U246 as \
power series of  s123, s125, s126, z, p3 which is convergent in a \
neighborhood of any point of the flipping  and the flipped loci. 
\
\>", "Text",
