Cell["\<\
The remaining coordinates : s123, s125, s126, z, p3 
                                       weights : -2, -1, 1, 1, 7
                                       The weight of the equation: 7-2==5
The flipping locus : s123 == s125 == 0
The flipped locus : z == p3  == s126 == 0\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9836477845871677`*^9, 3.9836478205655136`*^9}, {
