Cell["\<\
We check the singularity of the affine hypersurface Hyp501 == 0 near the \
flipped locus by the Jacobian criterion . Since Hyp501==0 contains the \
flipped locus z==p3==s126==0, we may regard U246 as constant 1 to apply the \
Jacobian criterion near the flipped locus.
\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.983648593344118*^9, 3.983648680460785*^9}, {
